###Crestron Device Discovery Script
###Script will call IP addresses from list and gather device information via autodiscovery 
write-host @"  



 ██████╗██████╗ ███████╗███████╗████████╗███████╗██╗███╗   ██╗██████╗ ███████╗██████╗ 
